name: Henreader
description:
An 8 vector embedding that emulates the style of a particular Japanese artist, trained on the NAI model. V1.0 is recommended version.

You may notice in the image metadata different variations, like 'henreader-8' and 'henreader girl'. It's all the same embed renamed for various testing purposes, such as training the same dataset on different initialization tokens and at different sizes; the presented embedding was the best result.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Working on another embedding, I found that 3-4k steps may result in overtraining. While I had no issues with V1 of the Henreader TI, this is an alternative version with half as much training for those who'd prefer it.
